# Test Automation Roadmap

## Vision
Gradually introduce automation to improve efficiency and coverage.

## Phase 1 – Preparation
- Identify automation candidates
- Select tools (Selenium / Cypress / Playwright)
- Define framework structure

## Phase 2 – Implementation
- Automate high priority regression cases
- Build stable test suites
- Integrate with CI pipeline

## Phase 3 – Expansion
- API automation
- Performance automation
- Full CI/CD integration
